The brand new 2013 monsterpiece by UK's finest purveyors of Orchestral Funeral Doom coming as a 1.000 hand-numbered copies deluxe Digifile CD with a second, bonus, CD featuring no less than SIX bonus tracks (the "Awoken by Crows" and "The Deceit" EPs). Get it before it's gone!

-----------------------------

One of 2012's best releases according to many publications (incl. VS-Webzine, Thrashocore and many others) is back on stock at long last (a few copies of the 100 copies limited edition DIY boxsets are still available, though). Get this masterpiece of Orchestral Funeral Doom NOW!
